{
  "stem": "214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If they had a son or a daughter, or an uncle or whoever lived in Warsaw, many of the people went to Warsaw, not knowing, you know, what will follow.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And-- and some other places, and again from the small community around Lodz, the Germans began already deporting people to, you know, to-- create a large Jewish center, and those Jewish centers became those big ghettos.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Lodz, Warsaw, Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the advice of my aunt was that we should definitely not-- not go to-- look for a place in the ghetto, because it was really-- it was so pathetic.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember one day I met one of my teachers who was a married woman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was a lovely person.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was so-- she was rushing, and I-- I always asked how are you-- I mean, how are you managing?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She said, I have to find a place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had two small children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have to find a place in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was a slummy part of most cities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- going back to us, so my aunt advised that little by little-- you know, my mother, my father, my little sister-- they should all start smuggling themselves to Skierniewice.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They found us an apartment in Skierniewice, and there immediately developed a smuggling deal, you know, because there was an actual frontier between-- between Lodz and [INAUDIBLE] because of that incorporation.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that as long as the ghetto is not closed, as long as the deadline isn't there yet, two of us should remain in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe things will change.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "See, one-- when I think of it now, that-- how did one know?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
